    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In computing, a localized network consisting of hardware and software links between computers, servers, printers, and other peripheral devices. Usually confined to an office or small physically defined area such as a college campus.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
